@startuml review_05_observability_evaluation
!pragma layout smetana
title 05 Observability, Evaluation, and Review Slices

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Arial"
skinparam ArrowColor #334155

package "Runtime emitters" {
  class PythonResearchHarnessClient #DBEAFE
  class ResearchHarnessService #DCFCE7
  class ResearchRunContext #DCFCE7 {
    +model_call_count
    +prompt_tokens
    +completion_tokens
    +model_latency_ms
    +state_snapshot()
  }
  class ReadingCorpusTools #DCFCE7
  class AgentsSdkHarnessRuntime #DCFCE7
}

package "Per-run capture" {
  class EvalRecorder #FEF3C7 {
    +append(kind, operation_id, payload, attempt)
    +finish(result)
  }
  class "events.jsonl" as events <<artifact>> #FEF3C7
  class "result.json" as result <<artifact>> #FEF3C7
}

package "Java product traces" {
  interface ProductTraceSink #EEF2FF
  class AsyncDiskProductTraceSink #EEF2FF
  class ReadingResearchTrace #EEF2FF
  class ReadingTurnArtifacts #EEF2FF
  class ReadingStatePatch #EEF2FF
  class ProductTurnResult #EEF2FF
}

package "Offline evaluation" {
  class GoldenCase #F8FAFC
  class GoldenJavaCorpusReader #F8FAFC
  class BehaviorScorer #F8FAFC {
    +score_case(dataset, case, run)
    +score_dataset(dataset, runs)
  }
  class FactAssertions #F8FAFC
  class JudgeModel #F8FAFC
  class "score_report.json" as scoreReport <<artifact>> #F8FAFC
}

PythonResearchHarnessClient --> ResearchHarnessService : stream progress/result
ResearchHarnessService --> AgentsSdkHarnessRuntime
AgentsSdkHarnessRuntime --> ResearchRunContext : model, token, latency totals
AgentsSdkHarnessRuntime --> EvalRecorder : transport + final submission events
ReadingCorpusTools --> EvalRecorder : tool args/results + before/after auth state
EvalRecorder --> events : append-only, sequenced, fsync
EvalRecorder --> result : atomic final write

PythonResearchHarnessClient --> ProductTurnResult : map answer/citations/usage/trace
ProductTurnResult --> ReadingResearchTrace
ProductTurnResult --> ReadingTurnArtifacts
ProductTurnResult --> ReadingStatePatch
ProductTraceSink <|.. AsyncDiskProductTraceSink
ReadingResearchTrace --> ProductTraceSink

GoldenCase --> GoldenJavaCorpusReader : product paper map
GoldenJavaCorpusReader --> ResearchHarnessService : same Java/Qdrant corpus path
BehaviorScorer --> GoldenCase
BehaviorScorer --> FactAssertions
BehaviorScorer --> scoreReport
JudgeModel ..> scoreReport : calibrated supplement

note right of EvalRecorder
Capture is sensitive local data:
questions, tool payloads, model traffic, and paper text.
end note

note bottom of BehaviorScorer
Scores Candidate, Read, Cited, grounding, outcome, content, trace, and efficiency.
Hard pass is not just answer wording.
end note

note bottom of ProductTraceSink
Trace, cache, and eval failures are diagnostic failures.
They must not change authorization or accepted product answers.
end note
@enduml
